# === Claude harness + internal docs/strategy (never ship to public repo) ===
# Public project documentation lives in the GitHub Wiki, NOT in this repo.
# Everything under docs/ is internal working state (plans, backlog, instructions,
# private analysis, progress logs) and must never reach the public mirror.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
description.md
docs/
# safety net for any future *CLAUDE*.md outside the above
CLAUDE-*.md
*-CLAUDE.md
claude-*.md
*-claude.md
